homeTitle.message: Faʻapipiʻi Firefox Addons I Google Chrome

homeSubtitle.message: Faʻataʻitaʻi firefox faʻaopoopoga i Chrome, Opera ma isi Chromium faʻavae suʻesuʻe.

homeCtaHelpText.message: Lagolago lagolago: crx, zip pe xpi

installerStepDownloadBodyText.message: Foxified o loʻo downloadina ma sauni lau faʻaopoopoga mo le faʻapipiʻiina. Faʻatali mo ni nai taimi mo le download e maeʻa.

installerStepInstallationWarning.message: Foxified e le lagolagoina API uma e manaʻomia mo lenei addon. Lenei o le a gagau ai nisi addon aoga.

installerStepCompleteBodyText.message: Foxified ua maeʻa ona faʻapipiʻi lau faʻaopoopoga. Faʻatali mo le faʻaopoopo fou e amata.

installerDownloadErrorMessage.message: Ua le manuia le laiga e laʻu i lalo le faʻaopoopoga.

installerExtractErrorMessage.message: Ua le mafai ona aveʻese mai faila.

installerAppIdErrorMessage.message: Ua le mafai ona aveʻese mai le ID polokalama.
